---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Echo4Ever - Your Private Digital Memory Vault" description="Preserve photos, videos, documents and life stories in a private digital vault. Control who sees your memories and when. Plans from $16.99/mo.">

  <!-- Structured Data -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebApplication",
    "name": "Echo4Ever",
    "url": "https://echo4ever.com",
    "description": "Private digital memory vault. Preserve photos, videos, documents and life stories for the people who matter most.",
    "applicationCategory": "LifestyleApplication",
    "operatingSystem": "Web",
    "offers": {
      "@type": "AggregateOffer",
      "lowPrice": "16.99",
      "highPrice": "35.99",
      "priceCurrency": "USD",
      "offerCount": "3"
    },
    "provider": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Echo4Ever",
      "url": "https://echo4ever.com",
      "logo": "https://echo4ever.com/images/logo.png",
      "contactPoint": {
        "@type": "ContactPoint",
        "email": "contact@echo4ever.com",
        "contactType": "customer support"
      }
    }
  })} />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 style="font-size: clamp(36px, 8vw, 80px); font-weight: 700;">Every life has a story<br />worth keeping</h1>
      <p>Echo4Ever is your private digital memory vault. Preserve photos, videos, documents and life stories and control exactly who sees them and when.</p>
      <p class="text-secondary" style="margin: 0 auto 24px; font-size: var(--font-size-subheading);">We help you keep your family's precious photos, letters, videos and voice recordings safe in a private place online - so your family history can be passed down and enjoyed by your children and grandchildren for many years to come.</p>
      <div class="hero__actions">
        <a href="/features" class="btn btn--outline btn--large">See How It Works</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__image">
      <img src="/images/couple-walk.jpg" alt="A beautifully curated archive of memories and photographs" loading="eager" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6 Features Overview -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center" style="font-weight: 700;">Six ways to capture what matters</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-secondary" style="max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 48px;">
        Your memories deserve more than a phone gallery. Echo4Ever gives you a proper home for every part of your story.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <div class="card card--feature">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/Life%20story.png" alt="Life Story" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3>Life Story</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Write about your childhood, lessons learned and the people who shaped you. Gentle prompts help you get started.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card--feature">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/Family%20tree.png" alt="Family Tree" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3>Family Tree</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Map out the people who made you. Add names, relationships and details and build it over time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card--feature">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/Photogrpahs.png" alt="Photographs" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3>Photographs</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Upload family portraits, holiday snaps, school photos - anything worth holding onto. Organised your way.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card--feature">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/Video.png" alt="Videos and Audio" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3>Videos &amp; Audio</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">A video of first steps. A recording of your grandmother singing. Your own voice, telling a story.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card--feature">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/Documents.jpg" alt="Documents" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3>Documents</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Birth certificates, handwritten letters, recipes, military records - the pieces that fill in the gaps.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card--feature">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/Clocks.png" alt="Time Capsules" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3>Time Capsules</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Seal a memory, set a date. A message for your son's 18th. A letter opened on your anniversary.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center" style="font-weight: 700;">Create. Share. Protect.</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-secondary" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 48px;">
        Your archive grows with you - one memory at a time. Start small, build over time.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <div class="card text-center">
          <h3 style="font-weight: 700;">Create</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Capture memories in whatever way feels natural - photos, words, video, audio, or documents. No structure required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <h3 style="font-weight: 700;">Share</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Invite family to view the memories you choose. You pick the person, you pick the moment. Change your mind at any time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <h3 style="font-weight: 700;">Protect</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Appoint a Heritage Custodian. When the time comes, the memories you've chosen are shared with the people you've named.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Privacy Promise -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 style="font-weight: 700;">Your memories. Your rules. Always.</h2>
      <p class="text-secondary" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 32px;">
        Every memory starts completely private. No public profiles. No social feeds. No algorithms. Your archive is yours and it stays that way.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/icon-private.svg" alt="Private" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 700;">Private</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Only you can see it. No one else. Ever.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/icon-family.svg" alt="Family" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 700;">Family</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Shared with the family members you invite.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/images/icon-legacy.svg" alt="Legacy" class="feature-icon__img" /></div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 700;">Legacy</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary">Kept safe until your Heritage Custodian shares it with the people you've named.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 32px;">
        <a href="/privacy" class="btn btn--outline">Learn About Our Privacy Promise</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container cta-banner__inner">
      <div class="cta-banner__image">
        <img src="/images/Baby%20feet.png" alt="Preserving family memories for generations" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="cta-banner__content">
        <h2>Start preserving what matters</h2>
        <p>You don't need to do it all at once. Add a photo today. Write a paragraph next week. Your archive grows with you.</p>
        <a href="https://app.echo4ever.com/signup" class="btn btn--primary btn--large">Create Your Archive</a>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-banner__image">
        <img src="/images/Graduation.png" alt="A curated archive of memories" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
